cn.campusapp.pan.lifecycle

接口 ControllerLifecyclePlugin

  • 所有已知实现类:
    AutoRenderControllerLifecyclePlugin

    public interface ControllerLifecyclePlugin
    Lifecycle plugin can be plugged into Pan, so it will observe the lifecycle and behave accordingly.
    It can only take effects with the help of controllers.
    The call(Controller, Class, Object...) will be called for each controllers in proper lifecycle.

    This means if your controller is binded in OnCreate phase, then there will be no call on this plugin because controller is not even functional at that time.

    Created by nius on 10/13/15.
